OL,3,CNCA officer jailed for theft of
OL,4,CBitcoin worth millions he'd had seized
OL,6,FITV News' Anna Youssef reports from
OL,7,Fthe sentencing of Paul Chowles at
OL,8,FLiverpool Crown Court.
OL,10,FA serving officer for the National
OL,11,FCrime Agency has been jailed after he
OL,12,Fstole close to #60,000 worth of
OL,13,FBitcoin from a Liverpool drug dealer.
OL,15,FPaul Chowles admitted laundering fifty
OL,16,Fbitcoin he'd seized from Thomas White
OL,17,Fin 2022 when White was under
OL,18,Finvestigation for running an illegal
OL,19,Fdrug-selling site on the dark web.
