OL,6,FWhite was later jailed for five years.
OL,7,FThe bitcoin Chowles stolen would be
OL,8,Fworth more than #4m today.
OL,10,FThe theft was only discovered when
OL,11,FWhite, now released on licence, was
OL,12,Fsubjected to a proceeds of crime
OL,13,Finvestigation and queried where the
OL,14,Fmissing currency was after it had been
OL,15,Fseized during the investigation.
