OL,6,FMerseyside Police opened a case,
OL,7,Fleading to the arrest of Chowles, 42,
OL,8,Ffrom Bristol who eventually pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to theft, transferring criminal
OL,10,Fproperty, and concealing criminal
OL,11,Fproperty.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for five years and six
OL,14,Fmonths on Wednesday 16 July and has
OL,15,Falready been sacked by the NCA.
OL,17,FDetective Chief Inspector John Black,
OL,18,Ffrom Merseyside Police's Force
OL,19,FIntelligence Bureau, said: "This case
OL,20,Fshould illustrate in the starkest
OL,21,Fterms that nobody is above the law.
