OL,6,F"When it became clear that one of the
OL,7,FNCA's own officers had stolen Bitcoin,
OL,8,Four officers conducted extensive
OL,9,Fenquiries to unearth a trail of
OL,10,Fevidence that Chowles had attempted to
OL,11,Fhide.
OL,13,F"He took advantage of his position on
OL,14,Fthis investigation to line his own
OL,15,Fpockets while devising a plan that he
OL,16,Fbelieved would cover his tracks. He
OL,17,Fwas wrong. "
