OL,6,FAlex Johnson, Specialist Prosecutor
OL,7,Fwith the Crown Prosecution Service's
OL,8,FSpecial Crime Division, said: "Chowles
OL,9,Ftook advantage of his position working
OL,10,Fon this investigation by lining his
OL,11,Fown pockets while devising a plan that
OL,12,Fhe believed would ensure that
OL,13,Fsuspicion would never fall upon him.
OL,15,F"Once he had stolen the
OL,16,Fcryptocurrency, Paul Chowles sought to
OL,17,Fmuddy the waters and cover his tracks
OL,18,Fby transferring the Bitcoin into
OL,19,Fmixing services to help hide the trail
OL,20,Fof money.
